<!-- Write styles in one palce But you will apply the style on various html element in body tag
    Internal styles are used by appling selectors 

    Selectors: should be writen in<style> (1) id selector (uses id) (2)class Selector(create a class) (3)Named selector (4)Grouped selector(h1 h2{font size italic})(5)Universal seletor (*{})
               ! important - it is used to make it important

               most used id>class>named>universal
Internal Styles 
->Styling goes to head tags 
->Html elements are sepreate in body tag
->these styles are only in one page/in the page where you write the styles

To create a class .is used to create a class>
->
-->
    <html>
        
    <head>
        <style> 
            .green-color{color: blue; 
            font-size: large;
        background-color: aqua}  
        </style>
        <h1>
        This is inline CSS</h1>
        <h2 class="green-color">agjbsd</h2>
        <h3>agjbsd</h3>
        <head>
        <body></body>

    </html>
